  m_text: "Before starting, you can choose your preferred quiz difficulty in the
    options menu. The difficulty affects the questions you will receive and the points
    you can earn.\n\nEach correct answer gives you points based on the question difficulty.
    Building a streak by answering questions correctly in a row increases your score
    multiplier. The longer your streak, the more points you earn. Be careful though
    \u2014 one wrong answer will reset your streak.\n\nTo start a quiz, explore the
    world and find the NPCs waiting for you. Each NPC offers a different quiz theme.
    Use the minimap in the bottom-right corner to locate nearby NPCs and discover
    new challenges.\n\nGood luck, and keep your streak alive!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
